Package com.ibm.watson.dsm.platform

Provides the basic framework for sharing data within or between JVMs.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IApplicationDescriptor
    Defines the information needed about an application instance.
    IDataAction<DESC extends ISharedDataDescriptor,DATA extends ISharedData<DESC>,STORAGE extends IDataStorage<DESC,DATA>,QUERYRESULT extends IQueryResult<DESC,DATA>>
    Defines the operation to be performed when a continuous query has been satisfied.
    IDataCondition<DESC extends ISharedDataDescriptor,DATA extends ISharedData<DESC>,QUERY extends IDataQuery<DESC,DATA>,QUERYRESULT extends IQueryResult<DESC,DATA>>
    This is a condition that evaluated local to where the condition is defined.
    IDataQuery<DESC extends ISharedDataDescriptor,DATA extends ISharedData<DESC>>
    Represents a query against data stored in a platform's data storage.
    IDataStorage<DESC extends ISharedDataDescriptor,DATA extends ISharedData<DESC>>
    Extends the generic read-only storage to enable write operations.
    IPeerSelector
    Provides a way to specify a sub-set of application peers within the application's name space.
    IQueryResult<DESC extends ISharedDataDescriptor,DATA extends ISharedData<DESC>>
    Holds the one or more results of a query evaluated on a remote platform instance.
    IReadOnlyDataStorage<DESC extends ISharedDataDescriptor,DATA extends ISharedData<DESC>>
    Provides read-only storage of data shared across one or more ISharedDataPlatforms.
    ISharedData<DESC extends ISharedDataDescriptor>
    Defines the set of meta-data associated with data shared into the ISharedDataPlatform.
    ISharedDataDescriptor
    Describes a portion of the application data, for example a database table or scalar value.
    ISharedDataPlatform<DESC extends ISharedDataDescriptor,DATA extends ISharedData<DESC>,STORAGE extends IDataStorage<DESC,DATA>,QUERY extends IDataQuery<DESC,DATA>,QUERYRESULT extends IQueryResult<DESC,DATA>,CONDITION extends IDataCondition<DESC,DATA,QUERY,QUERYRESULT>,ACTION extends IDataAction<DESC,DATA,STORAGE,QUERYRESULT>>
    Provides support for implementing a single distributed application instance.

    Class Description
    AbstractDataCondition<DESC extends ISharedDataDescriptor,DATA extends ISharedData<DESC>,QUERY extends IDataQuery<DESC,DATA>,QUERYRESULT extends IQueryResult<DESC,DATA>>
    Provides default implementations that define the condition as a non-aggregate with no remote condition.
    AbstractSharedData<DESC extends ISharedDataDescriptor>
    Can be used to provide some of the convenience methods, currently over the descriptor.
    AbstractSharedDataPlatform<DESC extends ISharedDataDescriptor,DATA extends ISharedData<DESC>,STORAGE extends IDataStorage<DESC,DATA>,QUERY extends IDataQuery<DESC,DATA>,QUERYRESULT extends IQueryResult<DESC,DATA>,CONDITION extends IDataCondition<DESC,DATA,QUERY,QUERYRESULT>,ACTION extends IDataAction<DESC,DATA,STORAGE,QUERYRESULT>>  
    AbstractStorageQuery<DESC extends ISharedDataDescriptor,DATA extends ISharedData<DESC>>
    Implements methods defined in IDataQuery interface and allows selection of shared data from the platform's IDataStorage instance.
    ApplicationDescriptor
    An obvious implementation of IApplicationDescriptor.
    ClassifiedPeerSelector
    Enables the specification of one or more peers by their classification.
    DataQueryMessage<DESC extends ISharedDataDescriptor,DATA extends ISharedData<DESC>,QUERY extends IDataQuery<DESC,DATA>>  
    DataResultMessage<DESC extends ISharedDataDescriptor,DATA extends ISharedData<DESC>>
    Used to send data resulting from a subscription back to the subscriber.
    NamedDataQuery<DESC extends ISharedDataDescriptor,DATA extends ISharedData<DESC>>
    Generic type that allows queries of ISharedData by name from the IDataStorage within the platform.
    NHopPeerSelector
    Enables the specification of one or more peers by the number of network hops they are away from the platform.
    PeerInstanceSelector
    Enables the specification of one or more peers by their IApplicationDescriptor.
    QueryResult<DESC extends ISharedDataDescriptor,DATA extends ISharedData<DESC>>  
    SharedDataDescriptor  
    TopologicalPeerSelector
    Gets a list of peers based on 1 or more topological relationships to a given app.
